import React, { useState } from 'react'; import './Profile.css'; const Profile = ({ user, onUpdateUser, onShowReport, onShowGames, onShowBreathing, onShowSleep, onShowAICoach }) => { const [activeSection, setActiveSection] = useState('overview'); // Sample data const sampleAchievements = [ {id: 1, name: "First Steps", description: "Complete your first journal entry", earned: true, icon: "📝", coins: 10}, {id: 2, name: "7-Day Warrior", description: "Maintain a 7-day streak", earned: false, icon: "🔥", coins: 25}, {id: 3, name: "Community Builder", description: "Join your first tribe", earned: false, icon: "👥", coins: 15}, {id: 4, name: "Meditation Master", description: "Complete 10 meditation sessions", earned: false, icon: "🧘", coins: 20}, {id: 5, name: "Therapy Explorer", description: "Book your first therapy session", earned: false, icon: "👨‍⚕️", coins: 25}, {id: 6, name: "Game Champion", description: "Play all mini-games", earned: false, icon: "🎮", coins: 30} ]; return (
{user.username?.charAt(0).toUpperCase() || 'U'}

{user.username}

{user.email}

{user.is_premium ? ( 🌟 Premium Member ) : ( 💎 Basic Member )}
{activeSection === 'overview' && (

Your Statistics

🔥 {user.streak || 0} Day Streak
🪙 {user.coins || 0} Coins
📊 12 Reports
💬 47 Chats

Achievements

{sampleAchievements.map(ach => (
{ach.icon}

{ach.name}

{ach.description}

{ach.earned && +{ach.coins} coins}
{ach.earned ? '✓' : '🔒'}
))}
)} {activeSection === 'journal' && (

Your Journal

{/* Journal component content would go here */}
)} {activeSection === 'shop' && (

MoodMate Shop

Use your coins to unlock themes and features

{/* Shop component content would go here */}
🎨 Themes
👤 Avatars
✨ Premium Features
)} {activeSection === 'tools' && (

Wellness Tools

)}
); }; export default Profile;
